




{"id":8732,"date":"2021-12-24T20:06:30","date_gmt":"2021-12-24T13:06:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/?p=8732"},"modified":"2025-09-24T15:32:16","modified_gmt":"2025-09-24T08:32:16","slug":"huong-dan-cach-tinh-kich-thuoc-inch-man-hinh-don-gian","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/huong-dan-cach-tinh-kich-thuoc-inch-man-hinh-don-gian\/","title":{"rendered":"H\u01b0\u1edbng D\u1eabn C\u00e1ch T\u00ednh k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc (Inch) M\u00e0n H\u00ecnh \u0110\u01a1n Gi\u1ea3n"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_78 counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-custom ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\" style=\"cursor:inherit\">N\u1ed9i dung ch\u00ednh<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><a href=\"#\" class=\"ez-toc-pull-right ez-toc-btn ez-toc-btn-xs ez-toc-btn-default ez-toc-toggle\" aria-label=\"Toggle Table of Content\"><span class=\"ez-toc-js-icon-con\"><span class=\"\"><span class=\"eztoc-hide\" style=\"display:none;\">Toggle<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-icon-toggle-span\"><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" class=\"list-377408\" width=\"20px\" height=\"20px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\"><path d=\"M6 6H4v2h2V6zm14 0H8v2h12V6zM4 11h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2zM4 16h2v2H4v-2zm16 0H8v2h12v-2z\" fill=\"currentColor\"><\/path><\/svg><svg style=\"fill: #000000;color:#000000\" class=\"arrow-unsorted-368013\" xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\" width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" version=\"1.2\" baseProfile=\"tiny\"><path d=\"M18.2 9.3l-6.2-6.3-6.2 6.3c-.2.2-.3.4-.3.7s.1.5.3.7c.2.2.4.3.7.3h11c.3 0 .5-.1.7-.3.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7zM5.8 14.7l6.2 6.3 6.2-6.3c.2-.2.3-.5.3-.7s-.1-.5-.3-.7c-.2-.2-.4-.3-.7-.3h-11c-.3 0-.5.1-.7.3-.2.2-.3.5-.3.7s.1.5.3.7z\"\/><\/svg><\/span><\/span><\/span><\/a><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/huong-dan-cach-tinh-kich-thuoc-inch-man-hinh-don-gian\/#inch_la_gi_cach_quy_doi_don_vi_sang_inch\" >Inch l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00e1ch quy \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb sang inch<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/huong-dan-cach-tinh-kich-thuoc-inch-man-hinh-don-gian\/#tong_hop_cac_cach_tinh_inch_man_hinh_cac_thiet_bi_dien_tu\" >T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n<p>Ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng nghe v\u1ec1 tivi 32 inch, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh m\u00e1y t\u00ednh 14 inch, &#8230; nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft <em><b>c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh<\/b><\/em> th\u1ebf n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng? b\u1edfi m\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc ri\u00eang. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi INNO chia s\u1ebb cho b\u1ea1n c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ed5i ra \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb inch c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch \u0111o v\u00e0 t\u00ednh k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, tivi, laptop c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh kh\u00e1c ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u1edf b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft n\u00e0y nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"1-inch-la-gi-cach-quy-doi-don-vi-sang-inch\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"inch_la_gi_cach_quy_doi_don_vi_sang_inch\"><\/span><strong>Inch l\u00e0 g\u00ec? C\u00e1ch quy \u0111\u1ed5i \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb sang inch<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Inch l\u00e0 \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i \u1edf n\u01b0\u1edbc ngo\u00e0i. \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111o n\u00e0y th\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea5y l\u00e0m \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb t\u00ednh\u00a0 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc cho c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed nh\u01b0 \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, tivi, laptop, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh,.. Hi\u1ec7n nay \u1edf Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111a s\u1ed1 ch\u00fang ta s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb \u0111o ph\u1ed5 bi\u1ebfn l\u00e0 cm v\u00e0 s\u1ebd quy \u0111\u1ed9 sang inch \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<p>Quy \u01b0\u1edbc: 1 inch= 2.54 cm<\/p>\n<p>T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ed5i sang c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb t\u00ednh kh\u00e1c nhau \u0111\u1ed5i sang milimet, m\u00e9t hay \u0111\u1ed5i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb sang inch.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"2-tong-hop-cac-cach-tinh-inch-man-hinh-cac-thiet-bi-dien-tu\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"tong_hop_cac_cach_tinh_inch_man_hinh_cac_thiet_bi_dien_tu\"><\/span><strong>T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p c\u00e1c c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed<\/strong><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><b>C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh<\/b> c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed r\u1ea5t d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng b\u1edfi s\u1ed1 inch ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a m\u1ed7i thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb. Tuy nhi\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi \u0111o v\u00e0 t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111o b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i vi\u1ec1n \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i hay laptop t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ebfn g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch \u0111o s\u1ebd ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<p>Thay v\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, b\u1ea1n n\u00ean \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t g\u00f3c c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn g\u00f3c \u0111\u1ed1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a n\u00f3. V\u00ec vi\u1ec1n \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i hay tivi, laptop bao gi\u1edd c\u0169ng s\u1ebd d\u00e0i h\u01a1n m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"2-1-cach-tinh-inch-man-hinh-dien-thoai\"><em><strong>C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i<\/strong><\/em><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean b\u1ea1n d\u00f9ng th\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111o 2 \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00e9o c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i xem \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c bao nhi\u00eau cm sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed5i sang inch. H\u00e3y nh\u1edb l\u00e0 \u0111o \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh k\u00e9o nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<p><i>C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c: (\u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i \/ 2.54)<\/i><\/p>\n<p><b>V\u00ed d\u1ee5<\/b>: chi\u1ebfc \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i Iphone 7 Plus c\u00f3 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i theo nh\u00e0 s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u00e0 4.7 inch. \u0110\u1ed5i 4.7 inch = 11,938 cm.<\/p>\n<p>Gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea1n h\u00e3y l\u1ea5y th\u01b0\u1edbc ra \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh k\u00e9o t\u1eeb g\u00f3c b\u00ean tr\u00e1i c\u1ea1nh l\u00ean g\u00f3c b\u00ean ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea1nh tr\u00ean. N\u1ebfu k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng g\u1ea7n 12cm th\u00ec l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c.<\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8734\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/content_cach-tinh-inch-man-hinh__2_.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"474\" title=\"\"><\/p>\n<h3 id=\"2-2-cach-tinh-inch-man-hinh-laptop\"><em><strong>C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh laptop<\/strong><\/em><\/h3>\n<p>T\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 <b>c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i<\/b>, gi\u1edd \u0111\u00e2y b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh laptop c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh bao nhi\u00eau inch nh\u00e9. B\u1ea1n ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh laptop v\u00e0 chia cho 2.53 \u0111\u1ec3 bi\u1ebft s\u1ed1 inch laptop \u0111ang d\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<\/p>\n<p><i>C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c: (\u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh laptop \/ 2.54)<\/i><\/p>\n<p><b>V\u00ed d\u1ee5:<\/b> B\u1ea1n \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh laptop \u0111ang s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 39,62 cm. T\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh laptop \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0: 39.62\/ 2.54 = 15.6 inch.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"2-3-cach-tinh-inch-cua-man-hinh-tivi\"><em><strong>C\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh tivi<\/strong><\/em><\/h3>\n<p>\u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb inch tr\u00ean m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh tivi kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ec1u d\u00e0i, v\u00e0 c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ec1u r\u1ed9ng c\u1ee7a tivi. \u0110\u01a1n v\u1ecb inch \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh tivi. Gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 <b>c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh laptop<\/b> hay \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh tivi hay c\u00f2n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh led th\u00ec b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o s\u1ed1 \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o c\u1ee7a m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh bao nhi\u00eau cm. Sau \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed5i sang \u0111\u01a1n v\u1ecb inch b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch chia cho 2.54 l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3.<\/p>\n<p>Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi tivi c\u00f3 m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh cong th\u00ec k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh tivi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh l\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o li\u00ean t\u1ee5c theo \u0111\u1ed9 cong m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh. H\u00e3y ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u00fang inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh nh\u00e9.<\/p>\n<p><i>C\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c: (\u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh tivi \/ 2.54)<\/i><\/p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-16670\" src=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Cach-tinh-inch-man-hinh-tivi.webp\" alt=\"\" width=\"900\" height=\"636\" title=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Cach-tinh-inch-man-hinh-tivi.webp 900w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Cach-tinh-inch-man-hinh-tivi-566x400.webp 566w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Cach-tinh-inch-man-hinh-tivi-768x543.webp 768w, https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/12\/Cach-tinh-inch-man-hinh-tivi-600x424.webp 600w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 900px) 100vw, 900px\" \/><\/p>\n<p><b>V\u00ed d\u1ee5<\/b>: B\u1ea1n \u0111o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed9 d\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e9o m\u00e0n tivi c\u1ee7a gia \u0111\u00ecnh m\u00ecnh l\u00e0 139.7 cm, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ed1 inch tivi nh\u00e0 b\u1ea1n theo c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9c: 139.7\/2.54 = 55 (inch).<\/p>\n<p>D\u1ef1a v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9 inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n tho\u1ea1i, m\u00e1y t\u00ednh, tivi,. s\u1ebd gi\u00fap ng\u01b0\u1eddi d\u00f9ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00ednh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh t\u1edbi m\u1eaft ng\u01b0\u1eddi nh\u00ecn \u0111\u1ec3 t\u0103ng hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 an to\u00e0n khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb th\u00f4ng minh n\u00e0y.<\/p>\n<div id=\"genai-translator-shadow-root\"><\/div>\n<div id=\"genai-translator-shadow-root\"><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ch\u1eafc h\u1eb3n b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng nghe v\u1ec1 tivi 32 inch, m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh m\u00e1y t\u00ednh 14 inch, &#8230; nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 bi\u1ebft c\u00e1ch t\u00ednh inch m\u00e0n h\u00ecnh th\u1ebf n\u00e0o kh\u00f4ng? b\u1edfi m\u1ed7i m\u1ed9t thi\u1ebft b\u1ecb \u0111i\u1ec7n t\u1eed s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 k\u00edch th\u01b0\u1edbc ri\u00eang. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng v\u1edbi INNO chia s\u1ebb cho b\u1ea1n c\u00e1c quy \u0111\u1ed5i ra \u0111\u01a1n&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":16670,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false,"inline_featured_image":false,"footnotes":""},"categories":[66],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-8732","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-tin-tuc"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8732","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=8732"}],"version-history":[{"count":4,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8732\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":16672,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/8732\/revisions\/16672"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/16670"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=8732"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/inno.com.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=8732"},{"taxonomy